title: AS Dikaki
text:
Association Sportive Dikaki are a <a href="association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Fougamou">Fougamou</a>, <a href="Ngouni%C3%A9%20Province">Ngounié Province</a> <a href="Gabon">Gabon</a>.
The team play their games in Mouila, the capital of the Ngounié Province.
The club won promotion to the <a href="Gabon%20Championnat%20National%20D1">Gabon Championnat National D1</a> in 2018.
